      "description": "We're listing this vehicle transparently as a car in poor condition, and we want buyers to have a fully honest picture before reaching out. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple scratches, dents, and possible rust or paint damage that goes beyond typical cosmetic issues. The interior is worn and may have tears, staining, or broken components. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it up to reliable daily-driver status; it is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs parts. It is drivable but should be inspected thoroughly before purchase. We are pricing it to reflect its true condition, and there is no attempt to hide its shortcomings \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
